      "title": "96 people infected with Covid",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Director General of Health Services announced in the afternoon that 96 patients infected with the 'Covid' virus were newly identified today (14).",
        "According to the report of the Director General of Health Services, the total number of 'Covid' patients reported in Sri Lanka is 668,012."
